ary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["The usual modern spelling of   Margery .  It seems to have arisen as the result of folk etymological association of the name with that of the herb <i>marjoram</i> (  compare  Rosemary  ). This word is of uncertain origin; its Middle English and Old French form was <i>majorane</i>, without the first <i>-r-</i>."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Marjory de Lennox was born in 1152, in Scotland. She married Gilchrist de Levenax, 1st Baron of Arrochar before 1230, in Scotland. They were the parents of at least 2 sons and 1 daughter. She died in 1213, in Forfar, Forfarshire, Scotland, at the age of 61."},"et":{"1152–1213":"1152–1213","1186–1263":"1186–1263","1230–1296":"1230–1296","1230–1300":"1230–1300","1213":"1213","1300":"1300","1296":"1296","1230":"1230","1263":"1263","1186":"1186","1152":"1152","Forfar, Forfarshire, Scotland":"Forfar, Forfarshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland"},"fi":{"1152–1213":"1152–1213","1186–1263":"1186–1263","1230–1296":"1230–1296","1230–1300":"1230–1300","1213":"1213","1300":"1300","1296":"1296","1230":"1230","1263":"1263","1186":"1186","1152":"1152","Forfar, Forfarshire, Scotland":"Forfar, Forfarshire, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland"},"fr":{"1152–1213":"1152–1213","1186–1263":"1186–1263","1230–1296":"1230–1296","1230–1300":"1230–1300","1213":"1213","1300":"1300","1296":"1296","1230":"1230","1263":"1263","1186":"1186","1152":"1152","Forfar, Forfarshire, Scotland":"Forfar, Forfarshire, Écosse","Scotland":"Écosse","lifeSummary":"Marjory de Lennox est née en 1152, à Écosse. Elle a épousé Gilchrist de Levenax, 1st Baron of Arrochar avant 1230, à Écosse. Ils ont eu au moins 2 fils et 1 fille. Elle est décédée en 1213, à Forfar, Forfarshire, Écosse, à l’âge de 61 ans."},"de":{"1152–1213":"1152–1213","1186–1263":"1186–1263","1230–1296":"1230–1296","1230–1300":"1230–1300","1213":"1213","1300":"1300","1296":"1296","1230":"1230","1263":"1263","1186":"1186","1152":"115